制派對許一直窮追猛打，擬向許提出譴責議案，褫奪其議席。昨日新民黨議員葉劉淑儀在立法會內務委員會提出，要求在本月23日立法會會議上，向許智峯提出譴責議案。民建聯黃定光斥許或太年輕就成為議員而自我膨脹，「自己錯，仲話人哋侵犯私隱，你對得住你父母、甚至對得住選你嘅人咩？」民主派反駁建制派其身不正，如私通前特首梁振英干預立法會、搞假學歷、漏報利益等，奉勸建制派得饒人處且饒人。"},{"pid":"990cbbfa3a69d51e2cb45f4b55344bf4081cfa34","tid":653730,"uid":12021,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T03:51:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f21580de9853e314be43c8acacb73f57f4e6d1fe","tid":653730,"uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73252173846e4040a4387483474b4c13e1c0b523","tid":653730,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T03:51:09.000Z","msg":"點解內容唔隔格"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T03:53:10.000Z","msg":"唔得咩"},{"pid":"4f203f31cfeb506160cb0dd8be0cc89b40de0104","tid":653730,"uid":23707,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T03:54:25.000Z","msg":"民主黨呢你老味 李柱銘去唔去保佢？"},{"pid":"e33c06536ae0fc2ffe4eb0b98b29426613f5e058","tid":653730,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T03:56:12.000Z","msg":"民主黨幾時正式割＿"},{"pid":"eabe5a884300ae36f9a9bb8c881b7341b016e4fa","tid":653730,"uid":132587,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T03:58:58.000Z","msg":"呢場鬧劇究竟完未<br />\n之前選舉會場比人偷電腦又唔見你地咁落力 <br />\n選民私隱重要過班議員行蹤啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6c4296e087a379c2850e65d419239cbda7f32b","tid":653730,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T04:00:10.000Z","msg":"民主黨最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592a60b71ebe3bed3a70876bcd2cff67d957a3a0","tid":653730,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T04:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JNI7pip.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJNI7pip.gif&h=21722eb8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c267aaaf5758c40832d366f723274abe18266b9","tid":653730,